<xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" n="sb;3;7253" targOrder="U" to="DITTO" type="reprint from">SB3,7253</xref></head><div lang="grc" part="N" type="edition"><div n="r" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>Πλο<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">υτογέ</supplied>ν<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ι</supplied>α τῇ μητρί μου πολλὰ 

    <lb n="2"/>χαίρειν. 

    <lb n="3"/>πρὸ μὲν πάντων εὔχομαί σε <choice><corr>ὁλοκληρεῖν</corr><sic>ολοκληριν</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="4"/>παρὰ τῷ κυρίῳ θεῷ. ἤδη ὀκτὼ <num value="8"/> μῆνες 

    <lb n="5"/>ἀφ᾽ ἧς εἰσῆλθα εἰς Ἀλεξάνδριαν, οὐδὲ 

    <lb n="6"/>μίαν <num value="1"/> μοι ἐπιστολὴν ἔγραψας. πάλι οὖν 

    <lb n="7"/>οὐκ <choice><corr>ἐχεις</corr><sic>εχις</sic></choice> με ὡς <choice><corr>θυγατέρα</corr><sic>θυγατεραν</sic></choice> σου <supplied cert="high" reason="omitted">ἀλλὰ</supplied> ὡς ἐχθράν 

    <lb n="8"/>σου. τὰ χαλκώματα τὰ <subst><add place="inline"><choice><corr>ἔχεις</corr><sic>εχις</sic></choice></add><del rend="corrected">τχις</del></subst> παρὰ σοί, 

    <lb n="9"/>δὸς αὐτὰ Ἀτᾶτ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ι</supplied> καὶ σὺ αὐτὰ παράλαβε 

    <lb n="10"/>ἀπ᾽ <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">α</supplied>ὐτῆς Ἀτᾶ πλήρης. <subst><add place="inline">καὶ</add><del rend="corrected"><del rend="erasure">ε</del>αι</del></subst> γράψον 

    <lb n="11"/>μοι πόσον κέρμα ἔλαβες παρὰ 

    <lb n="12"/>Κου<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">πι</unclear>νήρι καὶ μὴ ἀμελήσῃς. πρόσεχε 

    <lb n="13"/>τῇ <choice><corr>μηχανῇ</corr><sic>μεχανη</sic></choice> καὶ τοῖς <choice><corr>κτῆσί</corr><sic>κτησει</sic></choice> σου, μὴ 

    <lb n="14"/>ὀκνήσῃς καὶ μὴ θελήσῃς σκυλῆ-

    <lb n="15"/><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ν</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">αι </supplied><gap extent="8" reason="lost" unit="character"/><gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"/><gap extent="3" reason="lost" unit="character"/><gap extent="3" reason="illegible" unit="character"/> <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ἐὰν</supplied> δὲ μέλλῃ 

    <lb n="16"/>ἡ θυ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">γάτ</supplied>ηρ σου γαμῆσαι γράψον μοι 

    <lb n="17"/>καὶ ἔρχομαι ἐγώ. ἀσπάζομαί σε 

    <lb n="18"/>μετὰ τῶν τέκνων σου. ἀσπάζομαι 

    <lb n="19"/>καὶ τοὺς φιλοῦντας ἡμᾶς 

    <lb n="20"/>κα<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">τ᾽ </supplied><subst><add place="inline"><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ὄ</supplied>νομα</add><del rend="corrected"><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ο</supplied>νομαι</del></subst>. ἐρρῶσθαι ὑμᾶς 

    <lb n="21"/>εὔχομαι πολλοῖς 

    <lb n="22"/>χρόνοις. 
</ab></div><div n="v" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/><expan>ἀπ<ex cert="high">όδος</ex></expan> τῇ μητρί μου <expan>π<ex cert="high">αρὰ</ex></expan> <g type="x"/> <choice><corr>Πλουτογενίας</corr><sic>πλουτογενια</sic></choice> <choice><corr>θυγατρὸς</corr><sic>θυγατρι</sic></choice>. </ab></div></div><div n="meta.21351" part="N" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.21351" part="N" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date precision="low" type="textDate">ca. 297</date></p></div><div n="meta.21351" part="N" subtype="general" type="commentary"><p>Gehört zum Paniskos - Archiv. Zur Datierung vgl. BL VIII, S. 212.</p></div><div n="meta.21351" part="N" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl><bibl subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Mich.</title><biblScope type="volume">3</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">221</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">21351</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP"><series>0163</series>; <biblScope type="volume">3</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">221</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0163;3;221" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.21351" part="N" subtype="corrections" type="bibliography"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><bibl type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">VIII</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">212</biblScope></bibl></div><div n="meta.21351" part="N" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p><bibl type="illustration">JEA 13, 1927, Plate XXVI, Facsimile, gegenüber S. 71</bibl></p></div><div n="meta.21351" part="N" subtype="otherPublications" type="bibliography"><head>Andere Publikationen</head><listBibl><bibl subtype="other" type="publication">SB III 7253</bibl><bibl subtype="other" type="publication">Naldini, Cristianesimo 17</bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.21351" part="N" subtype="translations" type="bib